At Link, we believe in innovation, collaboration, and continuous growth.

We're passionate about turning challenges into opportunities and are on a mission to transform our clients into fully digital organizations by designing and engineering innovative technologies and building long-term, meaningful partnerships.

Technology drives us.

So, if you want to be part of a company that build their own products and solutions and create methodologies and services that align IT with business strategy.

Join us and help build the future, one smart solution at a time.

More than someone focused solely on test execution, we are looking for a person with energy, initiative, and the ability to positively influence teams and processes.

The purpose of this role is to help elevate quality practices, promote internal initiatives, facilitate the adoption of new approaches, and act as a bridge between QA, automation, and AI-supported solutions.

Responsibilities

Promote QA, automation, and quality best practices within development teams;

Identify continuous improvement opportunities in testing and delivery processes;

Contribute to initiatives related to AI applied to QA, automation, or process optimization;

Facilitate the adoption of testing frameworks, tools, and methodologies;

Work closely with technical teams and stakeholders to ensure quality and efficiency;

Support the definition of quality standards, governance, and guidelines;

Participate in the implementation and evolution of automation and CI/CD pipelines;

Act as a driving force within the team, promoting collaboration, knowledge sharing, and continuous improvement.

Desired Profile

Solid experience in QA Automation and/or Software Testing;

Knowledgeof automation frameworks and tools;

Experience withPython or other automation-oriented programming languages;

Exposure to or hands-on experience with AI/Gen AI (e.G., Prompt Engineering, APIs, intelligent automation, copilots, LLMs);

Experience working in Agile environments and continuous integration;

Strong communication and interpersonal skills;

Proactive, dynamic profile with the ability to drive and facilitate initiatives;

Interest in innovation, continuous improvement, and process transformation.

Benefits

Integration into a solid company with over 20 years' experience in the technology market;

Training and professional development;

Team spirit andmutual support, making you part of the .

Work-life balance;

Health insurance;

And much more...!


